## ARTICLE 9 — GENERAL PROVISIONS

**9.1 Severability.**
If any provision of this license is found to be invalid or unenforceable,
the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.

**9.2 Entire Agreement.**
This license constitutes the entire agreement between the Creator and
any User regarding the Language. No prior agreements, understandings, or
representations shall have any effect.

**9.3 Amendments.**
The Creator reserves the right to modify this license at any time. Updated
versions will be published on the official repository. Continued use of
the Language after a license update constitutes acceptance of the new
terms.

**9.4 No Waiver.**
The Creator's failure to enforce any provision of this license does not
constitute a waiver of that provision or any other provision.

**9.5 Survival.**
Articles 2 (Intellectual Property), 5.1 (Contribution License Grant),
6 (Restrictions), and 7 (Enforcement) shall survive any termination or
expiration of this license.

